g.text: Sends HTTP request to list the default patients list
This part will behave the same way as the representation below
but without any filters being applied.
Sends HTTP request to list the patients with filters
This will return a queryable list of all patients.
This means that other queries can be chained
to this one in order to filter the patients.
Returns the queryable list of all patients
Returns the queryable list of patients filtered by First
Returns the queryable list of patients filtered by Last Name
Returns the queryable list of patients filtered by Full Name
Returns the queryable list of patients filtered by Date of Birth
Returns the queryable list of patients filtered by Gender
Returns the queryable list of patients filtered by Medical Record Number
Returns the queryable list of patients filtered by Email
Returns the queryable list of patients filtered by Phone Number
Returns the final list of patients
